=== ALIEN_DICTIONARY ===
# id: 73
# title: The Alien Dictionary
# chinese_title: 异族辞典
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

A xenolinguist's workstation contains an unfinished alien-to-Chinese dictionary. The entries reveal startling parallels between alien symbolic language and Chinese radicals. Margin notes suggest the xenolinguist believed this was not coincidence.

* [Study the parallel radical systems]
  ~ gain_radical("言")
  "字" (zì) — character, word, writing
* [Complete some unfinished entries]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "典" (diǎn) — dictionary, classic
* [Download the dictionary to your datapad]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "存" (cún) — to save, to store
* [Search for the xenolinguist's other research]
  ~ gain_gold(20)
  "研" (yán) — to research, to study
